<ul>
  <li>Global Variables -&gt; nesting</li>
  <li>Structured Programming -&gt; nesting</li>
  <li>Types -&gt; not nested, nested only 2 levels deep</li>
  <li>Functions -&gt; (flat namespace, mostly)</li>
  <li>Namespaces -&gt;</li>
  <li>GC</li>
  <li>one-in-one-out, Calculators vs. Computers</li>
  <li>Sequencing vs. Asynch operation</li>
  <li>GOTOs -&gt; 1st Class Functions / CPS</li>
  <li>Epicycles - Copernicus, Gallileo</li>
  <li>O(n)</li>
</ul>

